parameters: Vita

\SE[37]Today is a day of doing nothing.... Yes, a day of rest.
\SE[52]It's not always about pushing yourself every day,
sometimes taking a break is also an important part of work...
Vita

\SE[44]Working too hard is a mistake that amateurs tend to
make... But I am an expert, so I won't make such foolish
mistakes... \SE[42]I will rest my body with moderation and
prepare for the next task...
Vita

\SE[82]Ugh...!? The resting is a bad thing disease is starting to
flare up...! \SE[35]A feeling of guilt for slacking off is
bubbling up...!
Vita

\SE[47]S-Stop it...! D-Don't put strange pressure on me...!
\SE[53]Ugh... My body... It's acting up on its own...!
Vita

\SE[44]But... I have to do my best...! \SE[64]Everyone is working
hard, so I have to work hard too...!! \SE[89]I have to work until
my body breaks...!!
Vita

\SE[52]N-No...! Taking proper rest is the most important...!!
\SE[35]Good work comes from a healthy body!!
Vita

\SE[53]Damn it...!! Even though I know that...! \SE[88]My body is
strangely compelled to start working!!
Vita

\SE[17]C-Calm down... Please calm down!! \.If I continue like
this, I'll work myself to death...!! \!\SE[83]Even though I know
it's a mistake...!
Laura
\SE[1]Oh, what's wrong? Were you fighting something?
Vita

\SE[68]...I'm saved. I was on the verge of dying from overwork.
\SE[69] I'm really glad you're here. Thank you...
Laura
\SE[84]R-Really...? I'm glad I could be of help.
Vita

\SE[4]Ah, are you going out by any chance? \.There's something I
wanted to ask you if it's okay...
Vita

\SE[3]Could you return the duck that I borrowed from Rebecca? I
accidentally forgot to return it. \SE[2]...Oh, if it's out of
your way, it's fine.
Laura
\SE[1]Rebecca, huh? Sure, I'll take care of it while I'm at it.

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The flames
here are the most comforting.
